00:14:42.640 --> 00:14:45.610
And the people who
love their homes and

00:14:45.610 --> 00:14:48.800
love the idea of owning a home--

00:14:48.800 --> 00:14:50.020
that gets that response.

00:14:50.020 --> 00:14:52.370
And then there's another
segment of people

00:14:52.370 --> 00:14:56.540
who don't like owning homes
and see value in renting,

00:14:56.540 --> 00:14:58.640
and they muster to the cause.

00:14:58.640 --> 00:15:02.210
