to call buckets.

00:24:53.380 --> 00:24:56.840
So a 401(k) is
not an investment.

00:24:56.840 --> 00:24:59.460
An IRA is not an investment.

00:24:59.460 --> 00:25:01.780
A TSP plan is not an investment.

00:25:01.780 --> 00:25:04.660
Those are buckets.

00:25:04.660 --> 00:25:06.880
In those buckets, you
hold your investments.

00:25:06.880 --> 00:25:10.300
Investments are things like
mutual funds and stocks

00:25:10.300 --> 00:25:11.219
and bonds.

00:25:11.219 --> 00:25:12.760
So those are the
investments that you

00:25:12.760 --> 00:25:14.780
choose to put in your bucket.

