to pick seven, eight, nine,

00:47:07.530 --> 00:47:09.790
maybe 10 industries.

00:47:09.790 --> 00:47:12.030
And inside those
industries, you want

00:47:12.030 --> 00:47:14.820
to pick two or three companies.

00:47:14.820 --> 00:47:17.730
And then you have a
diversified portfolio,

00:47:17.730 --> 00:47:21.780
because you really can't
physically and mentally

00:47:21.780 --> 00:47:26.580
follow more than 20, 25, maybe
the outside 30 companies.

00:47:26.580 --> 00:47:30.755
And that was considered to be
a well diversified portfolio.

00:47:30.755 --> 00:47:32.130
So when somebody
says to me, do I

00:47:32.130 --> 00:47:37.680
need to diversify
beyond 500 companies,

00:47:37.680 --> 00:47:39.060
I think you're there.

00:47:39.060 --> 00:47:40.470
I think you're there.

00:47:40.470 --> 00:47:42.502
