00:48:31.030 --> 00:48:33.750
So if you're investing
in the S&amp;P 500--

00:48:33.750 --> 00:48:39.420
and, of course, the S&amp;P
500 is 80% of VTSAX--

00:48:39.420 --> 00:48:43.140
you, by definition, are
invested in the world.

